dcfe","tid":208581,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:00:32.000Z","msg":"貴，但係又唔飽肚<br />\n一個餐三十幾，食完好似無食咁<br />\nM記廿幾，食完飽左<br />\n<br />\n態度差<br />\n明明已經收貴m記成10蚊，D態度仲差過M記，好似唔想你食咁<br />\n<br />\n會員無著數<br />\n已經食唔飽，KFC個會員制仲要差過人<br />\n我食M記有張卡/APP，基本上食乜都有得送，KFC食唔飽之餘仲要食夠100先有野送，又要ON99入分，買嗰陣唔記得入又無後補<br />\n<br />\n我嗰頭間KFC野食係得既，但我真係唔係咁想食，除非屋企人話要"},{"pid":"9d7985df3b152411ed960668c02b52e9fe080128","tid":208581,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:04:18.000Z","msg":"根本kfc應該先要俾人接手嗰個"},{"pid":"e6ff16ccf9532b53d256b7170b63f2ded6b3e903","tid":208581,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:05:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">成 個 地 球 都 知 你 係 乜 呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"eefd73f05bc95f98421a851faa41056b2251380b","tid":208581,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:07:23.000Z","msg":"因為係社企"},{"pid":"19913c4b97be380ec325d776de9447a4cabba2b4","tid":208581,"uid":76046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:18:06.000Z","msg":"好難食<br />\n食親都痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55034d8a8c97077c18361364dc0d414ac410d40c","tid":208581,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:32:15.000Z","msg":"唔好食"},{"pid":"601b0b5c0809a3586f35340baf2cab791fbdb30e","tid":208581,"uid":31423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T19:44:22.000Z","msg":"唔係手腳慢，係個system 慢，收銀要執埋餐，四隻手都唔掂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔請多啲人手，又唔學下M 記一邊點餐一邊攞餐<br />\n<br />\n最好笑係間間KFC 都長期大量吉位，但條隊排到出店外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇咁嘅能力去消化demand, 租咁大間舖嚟托咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b584a5b08f8037bf2cb6f9f48a37de20062c8ff1","tid":208581,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc